        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/juspay/nix-browser/blob/main/justfile\">https://github.com/juspay/nix-browser/blob/main/justfile</a></p>\n<p>Generally I try to keep <code>justfile</code> trivial, and move any complex scripts into being <code>writeShellApplication</code> package under a devShell's <code>nativeBuildInputs</code></p>",
